title: 258: Takeaways from the Divisional Round
itunes:title: 258: Takeaways from the Divisional Round
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into the wild divisional round weekend. Can the Jaguars defense carry them to the Super Bowl (13:28)? Are the Vikings the most complete team left in the playoffs (23:02)? Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series has you covered through the playoffs and into draft season.
